  <lyrics>[V1]
 Alajjpachar sarañajj
 Sinti sumapuniwa.
 Cristor iyawsasaquiw
 Take chuymamp sarascta.
 
[C]
 Munasiñamajj Tatay
 Sinti musparcañawa,
 Naya juchan jakeru
 Khespiyista ucata. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Juchan nay jacascáyát
 Llaquinacans phokt'ata.
 Cristojj munasiñapamp
 Tamaparuw irpjjetu.
 
[V3]
 Acapachan jaccasin,
 Jiwañ catutan ucqhas,
 Nayajj saraquimawa:
 "Jumaw khespiyasista".
 
 </lyrics></song>